OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFurther
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, some heavy and
OL,7,Fthundery. However, showers gradually
OL,8,Fbecoming more focused across northern
OL,9,Fand western areas overnight. Otherwise
OL,10,Fthere will be clear spells. Breezy,
OL,11,Fespecially in the north, and chilly in
OL,12,Frural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FFriday will be a drier day
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells and lighter winds.
OL,16,FStill some mostly light showers,
OL,17,Fespecially in the north and west. Rain
OL,18,Farriving in the southwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
